exthheader.author: Ursula K. Le Guin
exthheader.description: Ged is the older experienced Archmage of Roke investigating with young prince Arren of Enlad a mysterious disappearing of magic. Mages can no longer do spells. They adventure far to the south, and are led to the dragons' islands in the west. Ged closes the wound in the world, but it takes all his power to do so.
exthheader.subject: Science Fiction
